## UI/UX Guidelines

### Accessibility
- WCAG-compliant design, ARIA attributes.
- Keyboard navigation and screen reader compatibility.

### Responsiveness
- Consistent responsiveness across devices (Tailwind CSS utility classes).
- Standardize UI components using shadcn-vue presets.
- Minimal customization initially.

### User Feedback
- Provide clear loading indicators and confirmation/error messages.
